}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== OEM Global Sun GL2554RT-KA0-B10 / GL2554RT-LA0-B10
This is a simultaneous 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz wireless router.
The default SSID may differ with different firmware revisions. The default SSID on v2.40 and v2.42 is '''dlink''' for 2.4 GHz and '''dlink11a''' for 5 GHz.
==Links of Interest== *[http://support.dlink.com/emulators/di784/ Interface simulator]

- OS: ThreadX JADE/Green Hills Version G4.0.4.0
